  <summary date="2021-06-09T14:54:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Police Officers Protecting Children Act

This bill specifies that certain active and retired law enforcement officers who are authorized to carry concealed firearms are not subject to the federal prohibition on possessing (or discharging) a firearm in a school zone.</summary>
